message.body: Hiiiii sister, whatcha doin?
Hi! I'm at the studio today. You at work?
I started swimming laps at the gym.
Yeah. Super bummed out today. I broke up w dawayne this morning. For the best though. Wasnt feeling super positive about it anymore.
What!?!
Oh man! In your unitard???
Are you okay?
How do your gym buddies like that??
Come up here this weekend
The pool empty thank god.
(1/2) Yeah, im fine... its only been 5 months so in hindsight, it hasnt been that long. Just a little disappointed. But I remond myself I have tons of other
(2/2) stuff to focus on that is more important right nos
Going to do my taxes tonight and say a prayer to the financial Gods that I can pay off lots of old debts this year
Man that's very positive thinking. I'm sorry :( still a sad thing I know.
I have a meeting with a financial advisor on the 12th!
She gonna do all my taxes
Oh awesome!! Give me the inside tips whe. You know them. Haha
My taxes are so easy, I dont think I could if I itemized like you have to that gets complicated w grants and all
Yeah all my freelance stuff is not taxed so I'm scared
I saved though
Good!!
I made 41k this year (before taxes)
As soon as I get mine back, I will come up for the weekend. And go to the Y to boost my self esteem. Hahaha
Wow!!! Thats awesome lnz!
I made 31k
I know that's not a ton but for an artist it seems good!
Haha
Yeah! I want you to come up and go shopping and to the Y
Hey that's good!
Together we would have made 72k
Dang
That's high class lol
More than our parents combined! We movin up
Hahaha
Mom made 16k last year I think
That's more than I thought actually
All from subbing?
I told sade I was going to marry her for tax purposes and she can be my travel buddy when I retire
I think 4k from child support
Lol I think that is a good idea.
I see
I need to get a family lawyer in ct so I can change ilianas name. Ive been looking it up. Its such a shitty process
So what happened with Dawayne?
Oh man I can't even imagine
I just have trust issues. With him living in Herndon, it didnt make it easier and its not fair to either of us to feel like that.
Aw man.
(1/2) Soccer season is about to start and I dont have the energy to juggle everything. I want to focus on me. Eating good, paying off debts and making sure il
(2/2) i stays busy.
Yeah I think to some degree relationship should be supportive of the "me" stuff too.
(1/2) I was kind of mean when I told him I was done... he text me and I replied with " The customer you are trying to text is temporarily out of service. Msg 21
(2/2) 10" so he thinks I blocked him
Just makes it easier on me not to talk to him
Oh man! That's a good trick lol
If you asked him to give you space would he not comply?
Yeah. He was supportive of that stuff, he would give me space but the problem is that the space is what makes me have irrational thoughts...
They aren't irrational. You were in an abusive relationship
(1/2) Because hes so far, how do I know what is really going on?? I know its not fair to act like that but wouldnt it be foolish of me to keep living the same
(2/2) mistakes
If im not certain, I dont want to waste time and energy on something that could hurt me
Did he give you reason to think he's cheating?
You give yourself a break. Men need to handle our baggage better, you know.
(1/3) He would get texts when we were on video calls... he said they were other coaches, parents, family, etc but it just didnt feel right. I could be wrong but
(2/3) he did t go out of his way to prove it to me. He told me that I should just trust him. If I care for someone, I would go out of my way to prove it to the
(3/3) m so they are comfortable.
Help eachotha
What could he do that he wasn't doing?
(1/3) That was the question I kept asking myself. And all the answers were ridiculous. Im not going to check his phone like a child or make him explain himsel
(2/3) f day after day. I have trust issues and regardless of who's fault that is, it's not a healthy relationship if your happiness relies on someone proving t
(3/3) hemselves all the time
So the best decision was to walk away
Yeah. You gotta figure out what you want and need in a relationship.
And be able to communicate that
Takes time
Sometimes time by yourself
As soon as iliana turn 18, im becoming a cocktail waitress in vegas or a gypsy
This life is entirely too serious. Lol
I have similar aspirations lol
I think that a lot
I think we have black irish gypsy roots that speak to us subconsciously
Dont say anything to mom... she doesnt give the best love advice anyways... rather avoid that convo w her
(1/2) Some good news..... the governor approved my application to become a notary. I get sworn in like next week. Not a huge deal but looks good on resumes, i
(2/2) s grounds to ask for a pay increase at my annual review
Yeah moms the worst at talking about relationships haha. What does a notary do??
Can you sign legal docs?
Yup!!
Sweet!! Congrats!
Does the government pay you?
I got my tickets for Paris this week!
No. I can charge $5 per document but i am more excited because if I ever end up in court w david it looks good that I am a "government appointed public officer"
What the efffffff. I want to go!
Yeah that's awesome. Good thinking. They were spensive ugh
Whe. Are you going and what for
Dang, im jealous!!
Idk if I could do that flight though. I think I would need to be knocked out
We are gonna sleep on my friends floor don't be that jealous
It's only 8 hours not too bad
Red eye I'm gonna sleep
You send me Xanax though
Ha
Lmao ask the doc, seriously!! I need to double my dose next time
Haha
